nodes.text: Icindric caviar was a type of food. After a successful escape from Cantonica with Resistance fighters Rose Tico and Finn, the slicer DJ settled himself at the data console aboard their stolen ship and extracted a small tin of Icindric caviar from his jacket. The slicer offered some caviar to Finn, but the former stormtrooper didn't know what it was and declined with a shake of his head.
Icindric caviar first appeared in Star Wars: The Last Jedi: Expanded Edition, the novelization of Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi, written by Jason Fry and published on March 6, 2018.
